{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sabina, do something about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went over to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I says, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You've called me dirty Jew so many times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But do you realize when you call me a dirty Jew, you're belittling your God, Jesus Christ?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He is my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's my fellow Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when you say dirty Jew, you're saying Jesus was dirty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think I was 10 years old when I told him this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We became the best of friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is a way of overcoming, if you take the time to communicate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the other experience we had, Tony and I, my husband who is also an entertainer, we went to from Kiel, Germany to Norway on the Prince [?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Valiant ?] boat to do a show on crossing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1969.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way back from Oslo, Norway to Kiel, Germany, he had to do another show.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had an album.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, it got four stars in under Folk Album.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a little plaque never hurts, does it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CHUCKLING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this man, this couple, asked to purchase one, and would we sit with them?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we sat down with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was another young man with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could only speak with them in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I asked the questions about Germany and how things are going, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I asked-- as you know, I'm inter-racially married with a gentleman from the Virgin Islands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, do you have any problems in Germany for black people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Black people can live anyplace, go to school, no problem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we have another problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, what kind of problem do you have?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, we have a Jewish problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
